@startuml
title Playwright 登录业务流程技术时序图

actor "测试用例\nlogin.spec.ts" as Test
participant "Fixture\ntest-fixtures.ts" as Fixture
participant "LoginPage\nlogin.page.ts" as LoginPage
participant "BasePage\nbase-page.ts" as BasePage
participant "PageLifecycleMonitor\nlifecycle-monitor.ts" as Monitor
participant "Playwright Page" as PWPage
participant "BugCollector\nbug-collector.ts" as Collector
participant "目标系统\n/login" as App

== 用例初始化 ==
Test -> Fixture: beforeEach({ monitoredPage })
Fixture -> Monitor: new PageLifecycleMonitor(page)
Monitor -> PWPage: 注册 console/pageerror/response/request 监听
Fixture --> Test: 返回 monitoredPage
Test -> LoginPage: new LoginPage(monitoredPage)
LoginPage -> BasePage: super(page)
BasePage -> Monitor: new PageLifecycleMonitor(page)
BasePage -> PWPage: 获取 context/logger

== 打开登录页 ==
Test -> LoginPage: navigate()
LoginPage -> BasePage: navigate()
BasePage -> PWPage: goto('/login', domcontentloaded)
PWPage -> App: GET /login
App --> PWPage: 登录页 HTML/CSS/JS
PWPage --> Monitor: 触发 request/response/console 事件
Monitor -> Collector: report() if 4xx/5xx/JS/console error
BasePage -> PWPage: waitForLoadState('networkidle')
BasePage --> LoginPage: 页面准备完成
LoginPage --> Test: navigate 完成

== 表单校验 ==
Test -> LoginPage: isLoginFormReady()
LoginPage -> PWPage: 检查 username/password/submit 可见
PWPage --> LoginPage: 可见性结果
LoginPage --> Test: true/false

== 提交登录 ==
Test -> LoginPage: login(username, password)
LoginPage -> BasePage: fill(usernameInput, username)
BasePage -> PWPage: locator.waitFor + clear + fill
LoginPage -> BasePage: fill(passwordInput, password)
BasePage -> PWPage: locator.waitFor + clear + fill
LoginPage -> BasePage: click(submitButton)
BasePage -> PWPage: locator.waitFor + click
PWPage -> App: POST /login
App --> PWPage: 登录成功或错误响应
PWPage --> Monitor: response/requestfailed/pageerror
Monitor -> Collector: report() if 异常

alt 无效凭证或空用户名
  Test -> LoginPage: isErrorVisible()
  LoginPage -> PWPage: 查询 errorMessage 可见性
  PWPage --> LoginPage: true
  LoginPage --> Test: 展示错误提示
else 登录成功
  App --> PWPage: 跳转首页/返回 token
  PWPage --> Test: 后续断言或跳转验证
end

== 性能与生命周期断言 ==
Test -> LoginPage: getPerformanceMetrics()
LoginPage -> BasePage: getPerformanceMetrics()
BasePage -> PWPage: evaluate(performance.timing)
PWPage --> Test: loadTime/firstByte/domReady

Test -> LoginPage: getLifecycleReport()
LoginPage -> BasePage: getLifecycleReport()
BasePage -> Monitor: getReport()
Monitor --> Test: summary/details

@enduml
